### Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/

### Get all employees
GET http://localhost:3001/employees

### Search by name
GET http://localhost:3001/employees?q=ahmad

### Sort by salary descending
GET http://localhost:3001/employees?sortBy=salary&order=desc

### Get single employee
GET http://localhost:3001/employees/1

### Create new employee
POST http://localhost:3001/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "empId": "EMP008",
  "name": "Lee Mei Ling",
  "email": "lee.meiling@company.com.my",
  "department": "Operations",
  "position": "Operations Manager",
  "hireDate": "2022-03-01",
  "salary": 7500,
  "active": true
}

### Update employee
PUT http://localhost:3001/employees/8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "empId": "EMP008",
  "name": "Lee Mei Ling",
  "email": "lee.meiling@company.com.my",
  "department": "Operations",
  "position": "Senior Operations Manager",
  "hireDate": "2022-03-01",
  "salary": 9000,
  "active": true
}

### Delete employee
DELETE http://localhost:3001/employees/8

